attributes.action: Set the people free, Stop slavery, repeal all laws above natural, common law
attributes.additional_details:
The compulsory registration of births with government agencies is a practice that originated in the U.K in 1853. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Birth_certificate, before this people were born FREE MEN and WOMAN The certification is signed by the registrar, who is commissioned by the government or state agency, which is a permanent or semi-permanent organization
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Government_agency
We are not numbers or articles or objects to be traded. REPEAL ALL LAWS above COMMON LAW
attributes.background: People are born into slavery every day, people dont know, they are signed into contract at birth, this is illegal and every person should be aware of this, we are born as man and woman and then we become persons, objects owned by a company once the certificate is signed
